assets.name: HUXLEY Comic: Issue 1 - First Edition #2,854
assets.description:
Welcome to the world of Huxley.  Dive into the epic saga a decade in the making.  The first of six issues.

On a routine scavenging mission into the wastelands, Max and Kai uncover an ancient robot that could change their fortunes.....the discovery does not go unnoticed.

Head over to https://huxleysaga.com/comics/issue-1/first-edition/2954 to i) download the full digital version free of charge by the token owner, ii) redeem the physical comic, and iii) check to see if this issue has been redeemed yet.

asset_contract.name: HUXLEY Comics
asset_contract.description:
#Download and read your comic [here](https://huxleysaga.com/collection)!
> A decade in the making, Ben Mauro has finally unveiled his 6 issue graphic novel series - Huxley. This multi-faceted project represents a culmination of experience gathered over an illustrious career as senior concept designer and graphic artist behind gaming dynasties Halo and Call of Duty, feature films such as The Hobbit Series, Elysium, and Chappie, and successful NFT art series - Evolution.  Mauro’s Huxley saga invites readers into a post-apocalyptic universe, set in the desolate wastelands of a planet crippled by nuclear war - Fury-7 in Sector 217. Many fled to the stars to escape, destroying the space elevators and stargates behind them.  The remaining inhabitants were left stranded in the ruin they created…

>This is where the saga begins, and where the gripping adventure unfolds. What will be the fate of humanity in Sector 217?

Mauro’s Huxley saga invites readers into a post-apocalyptic universe, set in the desolate wastelands of a planet crippled by nuclear war - Fury-7 in Sector 217. Many fled to the stars to escape, destroying the space elevators and stargates behind them.  The remaining inhabitants were left stranded in the ruin they created…

>This is where the saga begins, and where the gripping adventure unfolds. What will be the fate of humanity in Sector 217?
